        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "22–29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Fury of the Jews. The Chief Captain orders Paul to be scourged, but on hearing that he is a roman, recalls the order in alarm",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
