      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "unto this word",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] It is probable that, though listening, they were not well-pleased at some things which they heard. Their pent-up feelings broke into instant execration at the hated word.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "and then lift up",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Rev. Ver.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " omits “then” for which there is no word in the original, but it is needed for the English sense, and would be therefore better retained.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "for it is not fit",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The best authorities read “It ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "was",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " not fit.” And this no doubt expresses the feeling of the mob. They had listened for a time, but when the speaker made mention of “the Gentiles” they were at once clear that he ought ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "long ago",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to have been destroyed. He had been all along a man who was not fit to live.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
